    <item>
      <title>台湾央行将采取温和紧缩措施应对通胀</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/rates-bonds/taiwan-central-bank-apply-moderate-tightening-against-inflation-2024-03-26/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[台湾央行周二表示，继上周意外上调基准利率后，将继续适度收紧货币政策，以抑制通胀预期上升。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/markets/rates-bonds/taiwan-central-bank-apply-moderate-tightening-against-inflation-2024-03-26/</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 26 Mar 2024 06:23:45 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>韩国央行官员称最终降息将刺激消费者支出</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/bank-korea-official-says-eventual-rate-cuts-will-spur-consumer-spending-2024-03-26/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[韩国央行董事会成员周二表示，韩国消费者支出将受益于央行降息，并补充说，国内需求对利率变得比以前更加敏感。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/bank-korea-official-says-eventual-rate-cuts-will-spur-consumer-spending-2024-03-26/</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 26 Mar 2024 06:06:09 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>印度尼西亚寻求更多证据证明爪哇虎可能不再灭绝</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/business/environment/indonesia-seeks-more-proof-that-javan-tiger-may-no-longer-be-extinct-2024-03-26/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[环境部官员周二表示，通过相机陷阱和广泛的 DNA 扫描，印度尼西亚自然资源保护主义者希望找到更多证据，证明爪哇虎（一种已宣布灭绝的物种）实际上仍然存在于野外。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/business/environment/indonesia-seeks-more-proof-that-javan-tiger-may-no-longer-be-extinct-2024-03-26/</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 26 Mar 2024 05:51:51 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>香港特首表示国家安全罪犯不太可能提前出狱</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/hong-kong-leader-says-early-prison-release-unlikely-national-security-offenders-2024-03-26/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[香港特首李家超周二表示，根据香港新的国家安全法，不让被判犯有国家安全罪的人提前出狱将成为“惯例”。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/hong-kong-leader-says-early-prison-release-unlikely-national-security-offenders-2024-03-26/</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 26 Mar 2024 05:50:31 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>官员称，武装分子袭击巴基斯坦海军基地造成六人死亡</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/six-killed-militant-attack-pakistan-naval-base-say-officials-2024-03-26/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[官员周二表示，武装分子袭击了巴基斯坦海军空军基地，造成至少一名准军事士兵死亡，安全部队在报复性开火中击毙了所有五名袭击者。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/six-killed-militant-attack-pakistan-naval-base-say-officials-2024-03-26/</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 26 Mar 2024 05:47:02 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>中国为应对低出生率和高成本，鼓励节俭婚礼</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/china-battling-low-birth-rates-high-costs-encourages-frugal-weddings-2024-03-26/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[在负责妇女权利的政府机构发表了一篇敦促婚礼更加节俭的文章后，中国的年轻夫妇计划举办“简单”的婚礼，而不是传统的数百名宾客的宴会，成为网上最热门的话题之一。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/china-battling-low-birth-rates-high-costs-encourages-frugal-weddings-2024-03-26/</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 26 Mar 2024 05:43:21 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>澳大利亚放宽了针对某些皮卡车的拟议车辆排放法</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/australia-softens-proposed-vehicle-emission-laws-some-pick-up-trucks-2024-03-26/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[澳大利亚周二表示，将放宽针对一些受欢迎的皮卡车的拟议碳排放规则，此前该国汽车游说团体担心这些变化可能会提高汽车价格并导致消费者选择减少。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/australia-softens-proposed-vehicle-emission-laws-some-pick-up-trucks-2024-03-26/</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 26 Mar 2024 05:06:55 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>受电动汽车进口影响，泰国 2 月份汽车产量同比下降 19.3%，皮卡车销量下降</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/thai-car-feb-production-drops-193-yy-ev-imports-lower-pickup-truck-output-2024-03-26/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[泰国工业联合会周二表示，2 月份泰国汽车产量同比下降 19.28%，至 133,690 辆，主要原因是皮卡车和更多进口电动汽车 (EV) 产量下降。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/thai-car-feb-production-drops-193-yy-ev-imports-lower-pickup-truck-output-2024-03-26/</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 26 Mar 2024 03:48:50 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>香港三月气温创下八年来最凉爽开局</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/hong-kong-swelters-record-march-heat-after-coolest-start-eight-years-2024-03-26/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[本周，香港气温攀升至 31 摄氏度（88 华氏度）以上，这是 3 月份从未有过的水平，而就在一周前，这个金融中心创下了八年来最冷的月份开局。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/hong-kong-swelters-record-march-heat-after-coolest-start-eight-years-2024-03-26/</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 26 Mar 2024 03:00:33 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>香港2月房价连续第10个月放缓，下跌1.7%</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/hong-kong-feb-home-prices-ease-10th-month-down-17-2024-03-26/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[2月份，香港私人住宅价格连续第十个月下跌，跌至2016年9月以来的最低水平，即使政府最近取消了对房地产市场长达十年的限制，预计私人住宅价格仍将受到抑制。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/hong-kong-feb-home-prices-ease-10th-month-down-17-2024-03-26/</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 26 Mar 2024 02:49:54 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
